<h2 id="1-mybatis-configxml파일이란">1. mybatis-config.xml파일이란?</h2>

<ul>
  <li>mybatis에 필요한 설정들을 기술하는 파일</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="1-mybatis-configxml-생성">1) mybatis-config.xml 생성</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Java Resources 아래 Source Folder 안에 위치</li>
  <li>DTD file로 생성</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="2-설정-태그들">2) 설정 태그들</h3>
<h4 id="1environment">(1)environment</h4>
<ul>
  <li>연동할 DB 정보 입력하는 태그</li>
</ul>

<pre><code class="language-javaStript"> &lt;environments default="development"&gt;
	
    &lt;environment id="development"&gt;
        
        &lt;transactionManager type="JDBC" /&gt;
        
        &lt;dataSource type="POOLED"&gt;
            &lt;property name="driver" value="oracle.jdbc.driver.OracleDriver" /&gt;
            &lt;property name="url" value="jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:xe" /&gt;
            &lt;property name="username" value="DB계정" /&gt;
            &lt;property name="password" value="비밀번호" /&gt;
        &lt;/dataSource&gt;
        
    &lt;/environment&gt;
    
&lt;/environments&gt;
</code></pre>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: center">종류</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">설명</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">transactionManager</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">JDBC : 수동 commit / MANAGED : 자동 commit</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">dataSource</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">POOLED : ConnectionPool 사용 O / UNPOOLED : 사용 x</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h4 id="2setting">(2)setting</h4>
<ul>
  <li>mybatis 구동시 선언할 설정들을 작성</li>
</ul>

<pre><code class="language-javaStript">    &lt;settings&gt;
        &lt;setting value="NULL" name="jdbcTypeForNull" /&gt;
    &lt;/settings&gt;
</code></pre>

<p>** 더 많은 name값은 공식 문서 참고</p>

<h4 id="3typealias">(3)typeAlias</h4>
<ul>
  <li>VO/DTO 클래스들의 풀클래스명을 단순한 클래스명으로 사용하기 위한 별칭 등록</li>
</ul>

<pre><code class="language-javaStript"> &lt;typeAliases&gt;
    &lt;typeAlias type="com.mybatis.board.model.vo.Board" alias="Board" /&gt;
 &lt;/typeAliases&gt;
</code></pre>

<h4 id="4mapper">(4)mapper</h4>
<ul>
  <li>실행할 sql문들을 등록</li>
</ul>

<pre><code class="language-javaStript"> &lt;mappers&gt;
    &lt;mapper resource="/mappers/board-mapper.xml" /&gt;
 &lt;/mappers&gt; 
</code></pre>

